## Overview

This analysis investigates the role of **SRGN (Serglycin)** in canine osteosarcoma (OSA)
using a four-layer computational approach:

1. **Layer 1** — Single-cell RNA-seq cell-type expression (GSE252470, 6 dogs)
2. **Layer 2** — Bulk RNA-seq TME correlation (DOG2 cohort, 198 dogs)  
3. **Layer 3** — Survival analysis (DOG2 clinical + GSE39055 human OSA)
4. **Layer 4** — Upstream TF regulon analysis (DoRothEA/VIPER)

